name: Mix pattern / 拼贴元素插画风格
description:
Unique model style, you will love it ~

独特可爱，不容错过的lora模型~

This is an illustration style lora, which can add some beautiful background and pattern to your pictures. The data set comes from nijijourney 100+ pictures, which can put beautiful clothes on the characters. It is recommended to use the flat paint illustration style model, and the model weight is free ~

这是一个插画风格的LoRa，可以为你的图片添加一些美丽的背景和图案。数据集来自nijijourney 100+图片，也可以给角色穿上漂亮的衣服。建议使用平面插画风格的模型，模型权重随意~
